HEADWORD: Silkweed
<hw>Silk"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the genera <gen>Asclepias</gen> and
<gen>Acerates</gen> whose seed vessels contain a long, silky down;
milkweed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

